info.summary: Ten multi-story 1x1 CS$$ Maxis-esque commercial shops.
info.description: Ten different buildings with multiple lots - these buildngs are all 1x1 multi-storeys, similar in size to original Maxis offerings like King Design and Tinkler's, Inc. All have standard stats and configurations, and all are tricked out with nightlighting to boot.
info.author: madhatter106
